comment._content: Accompanying note: "Kaye Batchelor, 1957 May Queen, poses in front of her eighteen May Court attendants, who will walk across Lewis Park Wednesday afternoon in the traditional May Party. Attendants to the Queen are left to right: First row: Kathleen All, Judy McMillan; second row: Judy Magnell, Shirley Oxbolt, Judy Smith; third row: Mary Lynn Scott, Abigail Fain, Barbara Kay Wrenn, Marianne Hartsfield[?]; fourth row: Esther Kirk, Patsy Sammons, Sheila Coldwell, Charlene Bevis, Teresa Long; fifth row: Evelyn Laing, Ann Moore; back row: Joyce Jackson, Margaret Sue Hooten."
comment.authorname: State Library and Archives of Florida
